casebody.data:
Terrilynne WALKER
v.
Wayne Charles WALKER and Gary S. Walker. No. 53P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2006. Gary S. Parsons, Hannah G. Styron, Jonathan McGirt, Raleigh, for Wayne Charles Walker. John W. Narron, Raleigh, for Terrilynne Walker.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 6th day of February 2006 by Defendant (Wayne Charles Walker) in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 4th day of May 2006."
